{"pid":"eb5a6ab5202e0971c4c21c4f171504b6429d6470","tid":2494632,"uid":258706,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"9046ace9e6c856a6a091a6868c3b086286f4ee7a","tid":2494632,"uid":370061,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T16:42:16.000Z","msg":"今次終於識玩"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T17:52:10.000Z","msg":"希望唔好似其他泛民組織咁臨陣退縮"},{"pid":"337353eb4e447febf946fb6a4d1b0553820aef94","tid":2494632,"uid":100986,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"eb5a6ab5202e0971c4c21c4f171504b6429d6470","tid":2494632,"uid":258706,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"9046ace9e6c856a6a091a6868c3b086286f4ee7a","tid":2494632,"uid":370061,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T16:42:16.000Z","msg":"今次終於識玩"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T17:52:10.000Z","msg":"希望唔好似其他泛民組織咁臨陣退縮"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T17:56:20.000Z","msg":"因為呢支政治汁有支共、港共以至狗力量撐腰，政治汁享受緊前所未有嘅特殊撐腰"},{"pid":"0264e2bcd36ab54d5b7f7f1493061ceecddc9b74","tid":2494632,"uid":100986,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"eb5a6ab5202e0971c4c21c4f171504b6429d6470","tid":2494632,"uid":258706,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"9046ace9e6c856a6a091a6868c3b086286f4ee7a","tid":2494632,"uid":370061,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T16:42:16.000Z","msg":"今次終於識玩"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T17:52:10.000Z","msg":"希望唔好似其他泛民組織咁臨陣退縮"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T18:43:25.000Z","msg":"好快藍屍會叫香港特衰政府點解唔立法叫公務員同死差佬（cctvb戇鳩警匪劇）強制打針，佢哋藍屍做細嘅完全唔想打針<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sorry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"808f3e7ecdb2dd85defcb2acdd3c68485eb75c8b","tid":2494632,"uid":100986,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T19:59:23.000Z","msg":"方向報功夫茶同藍屍讀者（忠誠鞭撻同忠誠監察香港特衰政府屍政）:<br />\n特衰政府同無能廢官變相威逼公司老闆迫打工仔打針可恥<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f6eb61b740af8734d19f7a806a44f098972fdeb","tid":2494632,"uid":268591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T20:33:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"212088afc5e6c66ee761b9fa22442fd36ad177c7","tid":2494632,"uid":100986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T23:35:54.000Z","msg":"<strong>職工盟收僱主反映 憂成「無良僱主」及衍生法律紛爭</strong><br />\n<br />\n蒙兆達表示，亦有僱主反映，憂成「無良僱主」及衍生法律紛爭，如員工接種後出現副作用，老闆會否因而「孭鑊」。他批評政府為接種人數達標，令員工成「犧牲品」，入侵身體式的防疫方法，與戴口罩的要求不同，違背自願接種原則。他指，如工會接獲投訴後，會製作「迫人打針」食肆名單，讓消費者參考。<br />\n<br />\n聽眾陳先生關注，如因僱傭問題接種疫苗出現副作用或嚴重事故，公眾最想知道因而產生的責任問題，由何方承擔。聽眾羅先生稱有經營餐廳，指認同平機會做法，勞資雙方應以協商態度處理，不應對立。"},{"pid":"431585442c97688cc5a400c3ea58dfba6e3f6ac8","tid":2494632,"uid":226296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"337353eb4e447febf946fb6a4d1b0553820aef94","tid":2494632,"uid":100986,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"eb5a6ab5202e0971c4c21c4f171504b6429d6470","tid":2494632,"uid":258706,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"9046ace9e6c856a6a091a6868c3b086286f4ee7a","tid":2494632,"uid":370061,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T16:42:16.000Z","msg":"今次終於識玩"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T17:52:10.000Z","msg":"希望唔好似其他泛民組織咁臨陣退縮"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T17:56:20.000Z","msg":"因為呢支政治汁有支共、港共以至狗力量撐腰，政治汁享受緊前所未有嘅特殊撐腰"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T00:28:25.000Z","msg":"針呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d7746f762914b0f02530ae83c7d2f73a6868dc7","tid":2494632,"uid":100986,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"431585442c97688cc5a400c3ea58dfba6e3f6ac8","tid":2494632,"uid":226296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"337353eb4e447febf946fb6a4d1b0553820aef94","tid":2494632,"uid":100986,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"eb5a6ab5202e0971c4c21c4f171504b6429d6470","tid":2494632,"uid":258706,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T17:52:10.000Z","msg":"希望唔好似其他泛民組織咁臨陣退縮"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04